{"tid":1856463,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"半夜突然好唔開心","createTime":"2020-02-01T15:41:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T16:02:12.000Z","uid":263213,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ecefdb29aa2626a7d04459b3e8c0a185f2047126","tid":1856463,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:41:39.000Z","msg":"睇睇下youtube諗番起<br />\n<br />\n依半年發生既事<br />\n<br />\n諗起被自殺、自殺同其他受傷、受苦、流亡既手足<br />\n佢地本身有機會拍下拖、行下街、同朋友一齊玩，過簡單快樂既生活<br />\n<br />\n但係就被黑警、同政權奪走左佢地一個個珍貴既生命<br />\n<br />\n佢地本身可能係系學校到，坐係隔離枱食飯、係課室訓覺、或者係我係籃球地抗波既任何一個人，就咁樣從我地既身邊永遠消失左，永遠無可能體驗番佢地原有既快樂<br />\n<br />\n梁凌杰、梓樂、彥霖等等一個個名浮現係我面前<br />\n我完全接受唔到個種手足死亡既悲痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n眼淚停唔到咁流落黎<br />\n<br />\n憑咩，個殺人政權憑咩奪走佢地既生命<br />\n而兇手仲可以高枕無憂，逍遙法外<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以應承我，唔好停止抗爭<br />\n直到有一日為佢地沉冤得雪為止"},{"pid":"371689278d70736f1a80a4132412a76445e45725","tid":1856463,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:53:27.000Z","msg":"ok push"},{"pid":"d1261282dade1f75b4f69693383b9074145c09a5","tid":1856463,"uid":181418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:55:10.000Z","msg":"唉。。<br />\n加油<br />\n香港人，共勉之<br />\n<br />\n搵個信得過既人，擁抱一下<br />\n發洩下會好d"},{"pid":"e50a6d9beb78e9ec6ffdc5ba5baebe040cedaa90","tid":1856463,"uid":307735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:55:13.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"3d1fac2504756a5bbc12e0d9dd96dfc74db14a9e","tid":1856463,"uid":99356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:01:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"50536f9d652c921c1a8500ed13151a66f3f2d3b5","tid":1856463,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20